   <h1 class="q"> Key Concepts in personal finance</h1>
    <p class="e"> some important concepts in personal fiance which an individual should be aware of while managing the personal finance.</p>
     <br>
        <div class="t">1. What are Savings:</div>
   <p class="e">Savings are the surplus of income over expenditure.</p>
  
