 <h3 class="t">What are the steps that an investor can take to avoid the adverse effects of inflation?</h3>
  <p class="e">Try to determine your "real rate of return", or the return you can expect after factoring in the effects of inflation. tTo mitigate the decrease in the time value of money, you can invest the money available to you today at a rate equal or higher than the rate of inflation.</p>
   <h3 class="t">8. What is Power of Compounding:</h3>
